h_Text_010_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10712,"index":17,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_010_c","CNzh":"索尼娅……！","TWzh":"索尼婭……！","JPja":"ソニア…！","USen":"Sonia!"},{"id":10713,"index":18,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_011_b","CNzh":"已经太迟了，劳鲁……","TWzh":"你來遲了一步，勞魯……","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}おそ>遅かったな ラウル…","USen":"You are too late, Rauru."},{"id":10714,"index":19,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_012_b","CNzh":"它已经是我的东西了！\n我会站在高处俯视你们……","TWzh":"這已經成為我的東西了！\n這股你們曾以一副高高在上的姿態……","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}われ>我は<Ruby={2:2}て>手に<Ruby={2:2}い>入れたぞ！\n<Ruby={4:6}きさま>貴様らが<Ruby={2:4}たか>高みから<Ruby={4:6}みくだ>見下し……","USen":"You took for granted the godlike power you had in\nyour hands."},{"id":10715,"index":20,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_013_b","CNzh":"理所当然地独占这份神一般的力量！！","TWzh":"理所當然般獨佔著的，如神一般的力量！！","JPja":"<Ruby={2:2}あ>当たり<Ruby={2:4}まえ>前のように<Ruby={4:8}どくせん>独占していた <Ruby={2:4}かみ>神のごとき この<Ruby={2:6}ちから>力！！","USen":"Do you now see the potential you squandered?"},{"id":10716,"index":21,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_014_b","CNzh":"这个女人就是你傲慢的牺牲品！！","TWzh":"那個女人是因為你的傲慢而犧牲的！","JPja":"その<Ruby={2:6}おんな>女は お<Ruby={2:4}まえ>前の<Ruby={4:8}こうまん>高慢ゆえの<Ruby={4:6}ぎせい>犠牲だ！！","USen":"As for her... She is merely the first victim of\nyour arrogance."},{"id":10717,"index":22,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_013_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10718,"index":23,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_015_b","CNzh":"你就带着自以为能控制我的悔恨长辞吧，\n劳鲁！","TWzh":"為做出自以為能控制我的不明之舉而懊悔，\n並帶著悔恨上路吧，勞魯！","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}われ>我を<Ruby={2:4}ぎょ>御せると<Ruby={2:4}おも>思うた<Ruby={2:6}おのれ>己の<Ruby={4:6}ふめい>不明を<Ruby={2:2}く>悔い <Ruby={2:2}い>逝くがいい\nラウル！","USen":"You tried to control me, Rauru, and you will die\nknowing that you failed!"},{"id":10719,"index":24,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_016_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10720,"index":25,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_016_c","CNzh":"加侬多夫！","TWzh":"加儂多夫！","JPja":"ガノンドロフ！","USen":"Ganondorf!"},{"id":10721,"index":26,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_017_b","CNzh":"劳鲁大人！","TWzh":"勞魯陛下！","JPja":"ラウル<Ruby={2:4}さま>様！","USen":"King Rauru!"},{"id":10722,"index":27,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_017_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10723,"index":28,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_018_b","CNzh":"趁现在，快去救索尼娅大人！","TWzh":"現在得先救出索尼婭大人！","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}いま>今はソニア<Ruby={2:4}さま>様を！","USen":"Queen Sonia needs you!"},{"id":10724,"index":29,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_019_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10725,"index":30,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_020_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10726,"index":31,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_021_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10727,"index":32,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_022_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10728,"index":33,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_023_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10729,"index":34,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_024_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10730,"index":35,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_024_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10731,"index":36,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_024_cb","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10732,"index":37,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_025_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10733,"index":38,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_026_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10734,"index":39,"key":"DmT_ZE_Birth_Text_027_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""}]}